{"tid":1933622,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"連爾街日報：十大富豪全洗牌","createTime":"2020-03-19T11:35:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-20T05:29:45.000Z","uid":346722,"like":1024,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"6dbeba32d6c2430dce088264037f76a21182573a","tid":1933622,"uid":346722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T11:35:53.000Z","msg":"連爾街日報：2020年2月尾發生的全球大股災，掀起了一場全新的經濟革命。從前我們認識的世界級富人在這次股災中損失極度嚴重，顛覆了人們對過往對「有錢」概念的認識。例如前股神巴菲特在裸泳的消息已經耳熟能詳。除此之外，其他富人也新申在這次危機中倒下來。讓我們看看股災之前全球十大富豪有誰上榜：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/my1TciP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmy1TciP.jpg&h=8b259241&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n經歷過一連串的財富大轉移之後，連登投資專家的獲利程度已經不能用任何文字能夠表達。絕大部份從前富人的財產在短短一個月內便像變魔術一樣轉移到一種新世界未來主人翁的手上。以下是最新富豪榜：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VKa8LEA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVKa8LEA.png&h=7944fbce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1 李嘉誠先生，眾人精神領袖，不用解釋。連燈富起來，他也自然富起來。<br />\n<br />\n2-9 排名不等 各有各獨特玩法 牛熊 十倍桿杆 正股撈底等等 不能盡錄<br />\n<br />\n在報道的最後，小編我受巴菲特先生的委托，希望香大家轉載他現在的感受<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BDR0BNw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBDR0BNw.png&h=27606ca9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WifTWNx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWifTWNx.png&h=dea6a5e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連爾街日報<br />\n2020年3月19日"},{"pid":"5c80574f6254352a63eae47fcba2fad812cb4bc8","tid":1933622,"uid":96743,"like":179,"dislike":5,"score":174,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T11:37:42.000Z","msg":"仆街<br />\n連豬都有錢過我"},{"pid":"b81b22a16cf8b9698c43c104602ac6f105dd854b","tid":1933622,"uid":27319,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T11:38:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im