9241&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n經歷過一連串的財富大轉移之後，連登投資專家的獲利程度已經不能用任何文字能夠表達。絕大部份從前富人的財產在短短一個月內便像變魔術一樣轉移到一種新世界未來主人翁的手上。以下是最新富豪榜：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VKa8LEA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVKa8LEA.png&h=7944fbce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1 李嘉誠先生，眾人精神領袖，不用解釋。連燈富起來，他也自然富起來。<br />\n<br />\n2-9 排名不等 各有各獨特玩法 牛熊 十倍桿杆 正股撈底等等 不能盡錄<br />\n<br />\n在報道的最後，小編我受巴菲特先生的委托，希望香大家轉載他現在的感受<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BDR0BNw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBDR0BNw.png&h=27606ca9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WifTWNx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWifTWNx.png&h=dea6a5e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連爾街日報<br />\n2020年3月19日"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T14:42:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b57df327ac322bd3955ca8c0344850b2c4d7426b","tid":1933622,"uid":336046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c77e696245c645c5f9148f66411390d49dacf79c","tid":1933622,"uid":346722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90c56e61d57d36c1f07526cea33f99fd7b13c638","tid":1933622,"uid":336046,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T11:38:56.000Z","msg":"又嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T14:07:41.000Z","msg":"開唔開心啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T14:46:47.000Z","msg":"就好似喺苦海中看見一紙救生艇，令我仿佛喺黑暗中看到一絲光明<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d1141f9adc686a65fec06c6825a8859391befd2","tid":1933622,"uid":352932,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T14:48:28.000Z","msg":"連儲局幾時成立？ 連爾街日報都岀埋 我真係太outdate la<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4